items.name: BOOKMARK
desc: The presentation jumps to a bookmark.

items.name: DOCUMENT
desc: The presentation jumps to another document.

items.name: FIRSTPAGE
desc: The presentation continues with the first page.

items.name: INVISIBLE
desc: The object renders itself invisible after a click.

items.name: LASTPAGE
desc: The presentation continues with the last page.

items.name: MACRO
desc: A star basic macro is executed after the click.

items.name: NEXTPAGE
desc: The presentation jumps to the next page.

items.name: NONE
desc: No action is performed on click.

items.name: PREVPAGE
desc: The presentation jumps to the previous page.

items.name: PROGRAM
desc: Another program is executed after a click.

items.name: SOUND
desc: A sound is played after a click.

items.name: STOPPRESENTATION
desc: The presentation is stopped after the click.

items.name: VANISH
desc: The object vanishes with its effect.

items.name: VERB
desc: An OLE verb is performed on this object.
